descriptionHtml:
[size=3]Skyrim Escape Anises Cellar Gamesave Blog

Hello and welcome to Escape Anises Cellar Gamesave. This is an escape and survive gamesave as well as a battle Gamesave to get your houses and property back from the Witch Anise.Â  You spawn as a Level 10 Female Redguard in a trap set by the Witch Anise. You first have to Battle Frost Trolls to get out of the Cellar, then battle some more outside of the Cabin in order to gain your freedom. After escaping you have a heap of places to explore and call your own, the only catch - you have to clear them of enemy spawn to gain access. After exploring the modified areas of this Gamesave, you continue on with the normal Skyrim Quests and you will be supercharged to take on any Dungeon, Dragon or Dirtbags that gets in your way.

See the ReadMe file for more details.


ShamanReaper57[/size]
